This well made short sword is several centuries old, but due to the lasting enchantments it bears, it appears as ready for battle as ever.
One of the first types of sword to come into existence, the short sword is a double-edged weapon about two feet long.  It is an economical weapon, and a favorite of archers and rogues.
Enchanted Short Sword

This finely crafted longsword is several hundred years old, but due to the lasting enchantments it bears, it appears as new and sharp as ever.
The longsword is the weapon most commonly associated with knights and their ilk.  There are many variations in the blade, but all are approximately 35 to 47 inches in length.

This mace is several hundred years old, but due to the lasting enchantments it bears, it appears new and ready for battle.
